    <item>
      <title>大选前德国 GDP 连续第二年萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/german-economy-shrinks-for-second-straight-year-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2024年，德国经济连续第二年萎缩，2025年也不太可能大幅增长，这凸显了德国新政府在2月份提前举行选举后面临的挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/german-economy-shrinks-for-second-straight-year-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:01:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于供应风险，IEA 预计今年石油过剩将减少</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/oil-surplus-narrows-for-2025-amid-new-supply-risks-iea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署表示，由于需求强劲和供应面临新的风险，今年全球石油市场面临的过剩程度低于此前预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/oil-surplus-narrows-for-2025-amid-new-supply-risks-iea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通胀缓解市场困境，交易员加大对英国央行降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示英国12月份通胀率下降后，货币市场纷纷预期英国央行今年将进一步降息，缓解了人们对今年困扰英国资产的持续价格压力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管特朗普征收关税，中国富裕省份仍着眼于 2025 年实现强劲增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/china-s-regions-set-bullish-2025-growth-goal-in-guide-for-nation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国五个最重要的省份表示，计划今年的经济增长率达到或超过5%，这表明尽管贸易逆风日益加剧，中国仍将制定雄心勃勃的国家目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/china-s-regions-set-bullish-2025-growth-goal-in-guide-for-nation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 06:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>480 亿美元债券投资者称东欧风险大于回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/-48-billion-bond-investor-sees-east-europe-too-risky-to-wade-in</link>
      <description><![CDATA[布兰迪万全球投资管理公司 (Brandywine Global Investment Management) 表示，东欧的政治和经济风险过高，以目前的收益率购买其债券是不合理的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/-48-billion-bond-investor-sees-east-europe-too-risky-to-wade-in</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际能源署预计今年石油过剩将减少，油价稳定在每桶 80 美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯制裁的影响持续显现，且国际能源署 (International Energy Agency) 撤回了对今年的看跌预测，油价基本保持在每桶 80 美元左右。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 23:31:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟考虑逐步禁止俄罗斯液化天然气和铝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/eu-considers-gradual-ban-on-russian-lng-and-aluminum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，作为针对俄罗斯全面入侵乌克兰而实施的新一轮制裁措施的一部分，欧盟正考虑对俄罗斯铝实施进口限制，并逐步淘汰俄罗斯的液化天然气。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/eu-considers-gradual-ban-on-russian-lng-and-aluminum</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 22:04:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
